{"tid":451940,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★沈大師 本週預測 10月30日 - 11月3日","createTime":"2017-10-29T16:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T13:09:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7855ef6aaff018cdca50cb573c38ca35a157fff0","tid":451940,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"本周的每日走勢推測：<br />\n<br />\n周一(庚寅日)：天干屬金地支屬木，金剋木之局，反覆偏好。<br />\n<br />\n周二(辛卯日)：天干屬金地支屬木，金剋木之局，走勢轉弱。<br />\n<br />\n周三(壬辰日)：天干屬水地支屬土，土剋水之局，偏淡為主。<br />\n<br />\n周四(癸巳日)：天干屬水地支屬火，水火交戰之局，反覆向淡。<br />\n<br />\n周五(甲午日)：天干屬木地支屬火，木生火之局，展開反彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/005155_a32496945eeab73510b350c2c45d6e18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F005155_a32496945eeab73510b350c2c45d6e18.jpg&h=30e02692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171030/bkn-20171030000728226-1030_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171030%2Fbkn-20171030000728226-1030_00842_001.html&d=jxB2QSzO9AW97skqhqm4HsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=658f2776\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171030/bkn-20171030000728226-1030_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"da01eab37b51b4a434df237b9a61cd0aa9c55913","tid":451940,"uid":118455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"準備買對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4342bb0e4b801db01237bd9488dd1c899ca13f2","tid":451940,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"你又點？"},{"pid":"483bd225b034df1a8525f261c1ceb6abdc54aacd","tid":451940,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又點睇？黑氣石</blockquote>"},{"pid":"777ccad4dcb204aedf416ef606f61c602beb8418","tid